Metadata: One in a series of ten "Newport's Commercial Fisheries" signs posted along the bay front in Newport, Oregon. The series includes: Salmon Troller, Tuna Troller, Bottom Trawler, Dungeness Crabs, Hagfish, Longliner, Pacific Whiting Midwater Trawler, Shrimp Trawler, Sablefish Traps, and Newport's Commercial Fishing Community.
